dct_description_sm: Iraq. Mudiriyat al-Misaha al-Ammah. Iraq. Directorate General of Surveys. [[Map of Iraq]: Zubaydiyah and Mahawil sections.] Alternate title: Liwa'ay al-Kut wa al-Hillah: Qada'ay al-Hillah wa as-Suwayrah: nahiyatay az-Zubaydiyah wa al-Mahawil. [Al-Kut and al-Hillah provinces; Al-Hillah and Sumayrah disctricts: Zubaydiyah and al-Mahawil sections.] Relief shown by hachures and form lines. Triangulation points are shown. Surveyed: 1938. Tribal lands and ownership are shown.
